  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "641d3d77054d99001c6be34e",
      "text": "日本語LLMに関する2つの問題",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679637881,
      "updated": 1679637913
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3d95aff09e0000693b6f",
      "text": "日本語LLMに関する2つの問題を混同する人が多いから絵にしたよ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679637910,
      "updated": 1679637910
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3d79aff09e0000693b6c",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/17f5a1e496eeeaac5100fbfc34b21785]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679637881,
      "updated": 1679637881
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3d79aff09e0000693b6e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679637881,
      "updated": 1679637881
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3d79aff09e0000693b6d",
      "text": "1の視点で「日本語LLMに意味はない」的な話をする人がいる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679637881,
      "updated": 1679638294
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3daeaff09e0000693b70",
      "text": "2の視点",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679637934,
      "updated": 1679638150
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3e17aff09e00007c5709",
      "text": "\t[GPT3では情報密度が逆転する]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679638040,
      "updated": 1679638040
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3ecdaff09e00007eb432",
      "text": "\t[日本語言語モデルについて考えたこと]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679638221,
      "updated": 1679638221
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3ecdaff09e00007eb433",
      "text": "\t\t>今後どんどん成長していくであろう「言語をまたいで思考するAI」に対するパイプの太さが重要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679638222,
      "updated": 1679638243
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3ee4aff09e00007eb434",
      "text": "  >「言語をまたいで思考するAI」は新たに発見された油田のようなもので、価値が湧き出してくる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679638244,
      "updated": 1679638257
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3eeeaff09e00007eb435",
      "text": "  >ここから湧き出してくる価値を、パイプの細い言語のユーザはあまり享受できない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679638254,
      "updated": 1679638259
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3e18aff09e00007c570a",
      "text": "\t[性能向上が頭打ちになるか、際限なく性能が向上するか]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679638041,
      "updated": 1679638047
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3e1faff09e00007c570b",
      "text": "\t\t頭打ちになるなら1の「規模の大きさによる差」が縮んでいく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679638048,
      "updated": 1679638090
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3daeaff09e0000693b72",
      "text": "\t[言語の力学]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679637934,
      "updated": 1679637935
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3daeaff09e0000693b71",
      "text": "　　現状、GPT4とは日本語でやり取りするより英語でやり取りした方が性能が良い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679637934,
      "updated": 1679638123
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3e56aff09e000020388c",
      "text": "\t[日本語の言語モデルは必要か？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679638102,
      "updated": 1679638494
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3fdfaff09e00007eb43b",
      "text": "\t\t>「別の小さいモデル」は無益だが「日本語に適したトークナイザー+αの層」は必要という話",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679638495,
      "updated": 1679638505
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3fddaff09e00007eb43a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679638493,
      "updated": 1679638493
    },
    {
      "id": "641da608aff09e0000b16aaa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679664649,
      "updated": 1679664649
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3feaaff09e00007eb43c",
      "text": "一つの解決策はこういうの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679638506,
      "updated": 1679664670
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3fb5aff09e00007eb437",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/4c9f57fda2d440f0c32a4d71c1b948d1]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679638453,
      "updated": 1679638514
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3fb5aff09e00007eb439",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1679638453,
      "updated": 1679638453
    },
    {
      "id": "641d3fb5aff09e00007eb438",
